hello,

First u download hamachi from www.hamachi.cc . Then you go in the triangle icon 2nd from the left Click it and then click join existing network. Then type the name and pass for the network know your in. Then go on the owners name right click and then click ping. Ones tahts done right click again an this time click copy adress then go to moparscape page at the side of the page there is file. Click it and do new ip and press ctrl+v. Then go to new port and type what ever is the port for server.

Know your in.

Glad To Help!
Good Luck!
